image_analysis.description: A photograph of the interior of a walk-in closet. The closet contains a gold-colored hanging rod with several wooden and plastic hangers. On the left, there is a white metal rack holding white towels. On the floor, there are two stacked white plastic laundry baskets. On the right, a white fabric hanging organizer with multiple shelves is suspended from the rod. A shelf above the rod holds folded white linens on the left and a blue and white patterned bag on the right. The floor is covered in tan or gold carpeting. A mirrored door is visible on the right side of the frame.
image_analysis.layout: Interior shot of a storage space/closet.
